      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Rub in, mix in the fruit",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Heat the oven to 200°C fan. Sift the {{self-raising-flour}}, {{baking-powder}}, {{sea-salt-fine}} and {{mixed-spice}} into a bowl. Rub in the {{unsalted-butter}} until the mix looks like coarse breadcrumbs. Stir in the {{caster-sugar}}, {{dried-currants}} and {{sultanas}}.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Stiff dough, rough mounds",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Beat the {{eggs}} with the {{whole-milk}} and pour into the bowl. Stir with a fork until the dough comes together in a stiff, shaggy mass; it should hold its shape when piled on the fork. Add another tablespoon of milk if it is too dry. Drop twelve rough mounds onto a lined baking tray, leaving 3 cm between each. Scatter the {{demerara-sugar}} over the tops.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Bake, 14 to 16 minutes",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Bake for 14 to 16 minutes; the tops should be deep gold and the rocky peaks should look crisp. Cool on a rack 5 minutes before eating; eat the same day for the best texture.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
